            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="0"/>
                <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>IEIVI<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="1"/>quaestura in p<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>rov</abbr><ex>incia</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="2"/>Asia functu<supplied reason="lost">s est</supplied> <lb n="3"/>incolae <expan><abbr>Avent<supplied reason="lost">ic</supplied>ens</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>ob <expan><abbr>egreg</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> eius erga se <expan><abbr>mer</abbr><ex>ita</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>patron</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ublico</ex></expan> cui singuli <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>adq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>univers</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> obligatos <lb n="7"/>se esse praeferunt <expan><abbr>adq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>etiam parum sibi vi<lb break="no" n="9"/>dentur praedicare <lb n="10"/>cura <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>iti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Nigr</abbr><ex>ini</ex></expan> Modesti <lb n="11"/>IIIIIIviri Augustalis
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Mehrere aneinanderpassende und verklebte Fragmente. Ein Fragment mit einem Teil der Inschrift vom Beginn der Z. 2 ist heute verschollen (VAE). Von Z. 1 noch die unteren Ansätze der Buchstaben erhalten. (B): Schwarz; Walser: Z. 1 nicht gelesen; Schwarz: Z. 4: Aventicens(es); Z. 5: erg(a); Z. 6: p(ublice) / cui; Z. 9/10: Zeilenfall fehlt.</p>
            </div>
